params.name: field_thank_you_one_time[0][value]
params.value:
Thank you for your Support!

[commerce_order:billing_profile:entity:field_first_name], thank you so much for your vital donation.

Thanks to your contribution we are able to provide shelter, protection and further support to refugees, asylum-seekers and stateless people.​ Donations like yours help to create success stories like Ashraf's story.

UNHCR is committed to ensuring that resources are used in the most effective way possible. For up to date information about UNHCR’s financial needs visit our Global Focus website.

If you have one more moment to spare, any shares on social media would also be a huge help! Spread the word and become a voice for those who are in need.

params.name: field_pi_form_message[0][value]
params.value:
Your privacy
By submitting this form, you acknowledge you are aware that your data will be used in line with our Privacy Policy. You have the right to withdraw your consent at any time by contacting us. If you are coming form the country listed here, by donating, you agree that your data will be shared with the local UNCHR entity.
